      • AdvancedSharedPreferences

        public AdvancedSharedPreferences(Context context,
                         java.lang.String filename,
                         java.lang.String value_delimiter,
                         int value_maxsize,
                         boolean debug)
        AdvancedSharedPreferences - Library for Android to extend SharedPreferences
        Parameters:
        context - - The context to use.
        filename - - Desired preferences file. (default: Preferences)
        value_delimiter - - The delimiter, that is used for splitting values. (default: µ)
        value_maxsize - - The maximal preference value length. (default: 8192)
        debug - - Print errors to console (default: false)
